snippet.title: HITMAN 3 - Launch Trailer (4K)
snippet.description:
Agent 47 returns in HITMAN 3 for the most important contracts of his entire career. The dramatic conclusion to the World of Assassination trilogy awaits... Available 20 January on PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, Stadia, Switch and PC. Pre-order now: http://hitman.com/buy

Music by BJARKE NIEMANN
Vocals by MINDY JONES
